<div class="content-frame-inner">Featured article<div class="heading-icon"><a href="/wiki/File:Main_Featured.png" class="image"><img alt="Main Featured.png" src="/images/1/10/Main_Featured.png" decoding="async" width="52" height="52" data-file-width="52" data-file-height="52" /></a></div></div><div class="content">
<h3 class="hiddenlinks"><span class="mw-headline" id="Guild_Wars_Reforged"><a href="/wiki/Guild_Wars_Reforged" title="Guild Wars Reforged">Guild Wars Reforged</a></span></h3>
<div class="floatleft"><a href="/wiki/Guild_Wars_Reforged" title="Guild Wars Reforged"><img alt="GuildWarsReforgedIcon.png" src="/images/thumb/a/ae/GuildWarsReforgedIcon.png/250px-GuildWarsReforgedIcon.png" decoding="async" width="250" height="73" srcset="/images/thumb/a/ae/GuildWarsReforgedIcon.png/375px-GuildWarsReforgedIcon.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ae/GuildWarsReforgedIcon.png/500px-GuildWarsReforgedIcon.png 2x" data-file-width="2298" data-file-height="671" /></a></div>
<p><b><a href="/wiki/Guild_Wars_Reforged" title="Guild Wars Reforged">Guild Wars Reforged</a></b> is a series of updates starting <a href="/wiki/Feedback:Game_updates/20251203" title="Feedback:Game updates/20251203">on December 3rd, 2025</a>, that focuses on improving the game experience for both new and returning players. It introduces new quality of life features, like a new quest tracking and direction system, support for higher display resolutions, HD skill icons, and graphical updates. It also brings support for controllers and Steam Deck.
</p>
<i><a href="/wiki/Guild_Wars_Reforged" title="Guild Wars Reforged">Read more.</a></i><div class="subscript"><a href="/wiki/Guild_Wars_Wiki:Projects/Featured_pages" title="Guild Wars Wiki:Projects/Featured pages">Featured pages project</a> • <a href="/wiki/Main_Page/featured_article" title="Main Page/featured article">Previously featured articles</a></div>
</div></div>
